Text About: Our October branch opened in 2005 after the success of our first restaurant in Sheikh Zayed. Following the success of our first branch in October, and later in Rehab and Downtown Cairo, we expanded to serve a growing customer base. This location was created to make it easier for customers who live far away or don't have time to come to us. We deliver food to all parts of Cairo and Giza quickly, and the food is always delicious. We are honored to serve you 24 hours a day.
